div.div: Saikyou no Ousama, Nidome no Jinsei wa Nani wo Suru?

After a mysterious death, King Grey is reborn as Arthur Leywin on the magical continent of Dicathen. Although he enters his second life as a baby, his previous wisdom remains. He begins to master magic and forge his own path as the years go by, seeking to correct the mistakes of his past life.
(Source: Crunchyroll)
Comedy, Fantasy, Romance, Slice of Life

The second season of Hataraku Maou-sama! MgRonalds best demon lord worker is back, climbing the corporate ladder to become ruler of Earth. But Maous plans of domination might need to be put on hold when a small girl claims to be his and Emis child! (Source: Crunchyroll)
Tensei Oujo wa Kyou mo Hata wo Tatakioru

"Who cares about being cute?! Rosemarie is a young girl who got reincarnated in the world of a dating sim. That game was famous for being a crappy game full of hopeless men! She has a bad feeling about it, but she has no time to waste getting upset about it! She's going to change the peculiar dateable character for the better and meet the man she really loves at all costs!"
(Source: POCKET COMICS)
Fukushuu Kansuisha no Jinsei Nishuume Isekaitan THE COMIC

Five years ago, in the middle of winter, Kosuke Kurono's beloved sister was raped and murdered. Ever since then, he has devoted his life to revenge. When he finally avenged his sister's death, Kurono had nothing left to live for, and he decided to end his own life, too. But instead, he was reincarnated into another world, and given the Black Magic wielded by the great heroes of the past. Being told that his sister might have reincarnated into this world, too, he set out to look for her!

(Source: Comic Ride, translated)
